      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to require the Secretary of Commerce to certify, before removing an entity from the entity list, that the entity is no longer involved in activities contrary to the national security or foreign policy interests of the United States and that removing the entity from the list does not pose a threat to allies of the United States.</title>
      </item>
